1️⃣ Title
# Azure Nautilus Migration – Day 1
Create Azure VM Using Azure CLI

## 2️⃣ Objective
Provision an Azure Virtual Machine using Azure CLI in a restricted environment where
resource group creation and discovery are not permitted.

## 3️⃣ Environment Constraints
- Azure Portal access is disabled
- Resource Group creation and listing are restricted by RBAC
- Authorized Resource Group is provided via environment variables

## 4️⃣ Resource Group Access Verification
The authorized resource group is identified using environment variables
available on the azure-client host.

